Toto je jediná cenná vec v tomto dome.

463
00:30:12,020 --> 00:30:13,670
Hadia pálenka.

464
00:30:14,360 --> 00:30:16,870
Ďakujeme.

465
00:30:17,730 --> 00:30:20,410
Zober aj tú fľašu.

466
00:30:21,530 --> 00:30:22,810
Túto?

